snippet.title: Cruis'n Blast Track Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out some of the tracks that will be in the upcoming Cruis'n Blast for Nintendo Switch. Cruis'n Blast is getting a digital and physical release on September 14, 2021.

You can learn more about the game right here: https://rawthrills.com/games/cruisn-blast/
